Fix warnings in animation and animationWithKeyPath: methods

updateRearViewVisibilityForFrontViewPosition: should update self.state the same way updateRearViewVisibility does.  Otherwise, the timing is off for the willChangeToState/didChangeToState calls to the delegate.
Fix setter, which is checking and setting _recognizesResetTapOnFrontView instead of _recognizesPanningOnFrontView.
Use of weak self to avoid strongly captured over-retained self in blocks

When adding a child controller to a container, it should call child's
didMoveToParentViewController, not "self"

Objective-C runtime can handle the message to nil. Now it has only one return.
Block indirection fixed

Change parentViewController check

This should be checking for existence, not non-existence, for self.parentViewController
isPositive only returns YES when  value > 0

isPositive only returns YES for positive values

not for zero.

Modified ZUUIRevealController to work on iOS 4.0 by overriding automaticallyForwardAppearanceAndRotationMethodsToChildViewControllers and the appearance and rotation methods. Changed both to iOS Deployment Target 4.0.
Revert code sign settings to defaults
Fix memory management: Don't set strong properties to nil in dealloc (which breaks KVO and can cause zombies) - instead nil out the ivars
Changed currentFrontViewPosition to be instance variable.
